elements honorific honorific Element
honorific &honorific.purpose;
&honorific.synopsis.gen; Description
An Honorific occurs in the name of an individual. It is the honorific title of the individual, such as Dr., Mr., or Ms.
Processing expectations
&format.inline; In an Address, this element may inherit the verbatim qualities of an address.
On some systems, Honorific may generate the trailing period automatically.
&honorific.parents.gen; &honorific.children.gen;
